::Kaiser::
       Recognizing the feint he turns slightly to the side and crosses his 
blades in front of the oncoming slash in a block that jarred his arms and set 
his rear foot back a few inches.  Quickly pulling one blade out of the block 
he lashes out, aiming the pommel of his blade at DeathSteel's face.
